    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, slice each of your <strong>chicken breast portion[s]</strong> into 3-4 strips</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>garlic </strong>(you'll use the rest later!)</p><p>Peel your <strong>ginger</strong> (scrape the skin off with a teaspoon) and chop (or grate) finely</p>",
