            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/839.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>cornflour</strong> to a bowl</p><p>Add the<strong> marinated</strong> <strong>chicken strips</strong>, leaving most of the marinade behind</p><p>Give everything a good mix up so the chicken strips are fully coated in cornflour</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/839.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/839.-step-6-x400.jpg",
