            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a high heat with enough <strong>vegetable oil</strong> to cover the bottom of the pan</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> coated chicken</strong> and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until browned and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>chicken karaage</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
